here are the endpoints:

 

Authentication API's

 

Register Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/auth/register

 

Login Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/auth/login

 

 

User API's

 

getUsers Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/auth/getUsers

 

viewProfile Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/user/:userId

 

updateProfile Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/updateProfile/:userId

 

uploadPhoto Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/user/upload/image/:userId

 

updateGeolocation Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/user/updateGeo/:userId

 

 

Location API's

 

sendLocation Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/location/sendlocation

 

nearby Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/location/nearby

 

 

Chat API's

 

newConversation Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/chat/new/:recipientId

 

sendReply Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/chat/:conversationId

 

getConversation Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/chat/:conversationId

 

getMessages Api : http://media-consultancy.com:3000/api/chat/getmessages/:userid